---
// Static collaboration illustration showing multiple users editing together
// Displays text content with colored cursors indicating real-time collaboration
import Cursor from "../generic/Cursor.astro";
---

<style>
  @keyframes selection-expand {
    0% {
      width: 0;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      width: 100%;
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
  
  .selection-animate {
    display: inline-block;
    overflow: hidden;
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation: selection-expand 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94) forwards;
    width: 0;
    opacity: 0;
  }
</style>

<div class="px-8 py-6 max-w-[65ch] mx-auto overflow-hidden">
  <h1 class="text-[1.75rem] font-medium text-gray-900 mt-0 mb-4 select-none">
    Q3 Product Roadmap
  </h1>

  <div class="prose prose-sm">
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Focus areas for the upcoming quarter based on user feedback and growth targets.
      <span class="selection-animate rounded-sm relative inline-block" style="background-color: #6eeb8333; animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        The analytics dashboard redesign is our top priority
        <Cursor name="Alex" colorId="green" position="top" class="absolute -right-3 top-0" delay={0.5} />
      </span>
      {" "}and should ship by mid-July. <em>Performance improvements are blocking the release.</em>
    </p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Key initiatives for this quarter include mobile responsiveness and
      <span class="relative inline-block">
        <Cursor name="Sarah" colorId="cyan" position="top" class="absolute -right-3 top-0" delay={0} />
      </span>
      {" "}the new onboarding flow. I'll update the timeline once we get design approvals.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Milestone Timeline</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-4 text-gray-700">
      <li>
        <p>
          <strong>July 15</strong> — Analytics v2 beta launch
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>August 1 — Mobile app soft launch to 10% of users</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          For detailed technical specs, see{" "}
          <span class="font-medium underline decoration-blue-600 decoration-2 text-blue-600">
            Engineering Specs Q3
          </span>.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>September 1 — Full mobile rollout</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Documentation and API updates for partner integrations
          <Cursor name="Jordan" colorId="gold" />
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Open Questions</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Need to finalize vendor selection for the new hosting provider. Budget review
      scheduled for next Tuesday with the finance team.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-4 text-gray-700">
      <li>Migration timeline and rollback strategy</li>
      <li>Compliance requirements for EU users</li>
      <li>Team capacity during August vacation period</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-0">
      Please add any blockers or dependencies I might have missed. Looking forward to
      shipping these improvements!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
